          "value": "<p>The @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} conditions from filth fever don't improve on their own until the disease is cured.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:14]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect ([[/br 1d4 #hours]]{1d4 hours})</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> Sickened 1 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead</p>"
